              "content": "生效日期：2026 年 6 月 1 日",
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 12,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "R9803",
              "name": "S",
              "fill": "$text-primary",
              "content": "1. 服务说明",
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "600"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "y3mpSp",
              "name": "P",
              "fill": "$text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "计件猫是一款面向中小型工厂的计件管理 SaaS 工具，提供报工、审核、工资核算、通知推送等功能。",
              "lineHeight": 1.7,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "J4shd",
              "name": "S",
              "fill": "$text-primary",
              "content": "2. 账号注册",
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "600"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "B0uT4l",
              "name": "P",
              "fill": "$text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "用户须使用真实手机号注册并保管好账号信息。同一工厂的员工与管理员账号关系经工厂管理员审核确认。",
              "lineHeight": 1.7,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "XNsKg",
              "name": "S",
              "fill": "$text-primary",
              "content": "3. 用户行为规范",
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "600"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "ek1yp",
              "name": "P",
              "fill": "$text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "严禁伪造报工数据、恶意篡改他人记录或盗用他人账号；一经发现，工厂管理员有权立即停用相关账号。",
              "lineHeight": 1.7,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "kRGdM",
              "name": "S",
              "fill": "$text-primary",
              "content": "4. 责任限制",
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "600"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "LLbmM",
              "name": "P",
              "fill": "$text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "本服务按现状提供。因不可抗力、第三方服务（如微信平台）异常导致的服务中断，本平台不承担责任。",
              "lineHeight": 1.7,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "dF5jT",
              "name": "S",
              "fill": "$text-primary",
              "content": "5. 协议变更",
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "600"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "m2z2k5",
              "name": "P",
              "fill": "$text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "本平台保留对协议的修改权。重大变更将通过站内通知告知，继续使用即视为接受。",
              "lineHeight": 1.7,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
